{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "来自深海的钟声第2话 海神之巫女",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "在福斯亚克，沙音与穆穆遇到了海洋之民\\n谢斯塔族，他们正面临着灭亡的危机。\\n沙音、穆穆和海洋之民的巫女\\n蒂亚娜一同打造了沧海之钟，\\n并向海神利维坦求救。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "很久以前，福斯亚克是一座\\n漂浮在海上的广阔岛屿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "1000年前的封魔战争之际，\\n大海受到圣域龙与魔神之战的\\n余波影响，海浪肆虐。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "岛民虽然向内陆求救，\\n却无人回应。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "于是岛民便下定决心，\\n放弃孤独又危险的陆地生活，\\n选择在海里活下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人们向海神利维坦祈祷。\\n利维坦抑制住破涛汹涌的大海，\\n将岛屿引导至海中。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "人们将利维坦视作神灵般崇拜，\\n通过自己独特的文化与技术\\n在海底建立起了国家。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "add_book_text",
            "context": "深海王国福斯亚克\\n和海洋之民谢斯塔族\\n就是这样诞生的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "据说这就是这个国家\\n和我们海洋之民\\n谢斯塔族的起源。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你们不仅能在海里呼吸，\\n还能和鱼说话，\\n真是一个神奇的种族。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "呵呵，说得我怪不好意思的。\\n谢斯塔族通过在海中的生活\\n完成了独具一格的进化。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "但谢斯塔族的繁荣也只是昙花一现，\\n渐渐地，人们开始为资源\\n与粮食的短缺而烦恼……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "原来是在这1000年里\\n逐渐变成这样的吗？不过，\\n这些问题总有人关心吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "是啊。我想人们的危机意识\\n是有所提高的。不过，谢斯塔族\\n与人类相比寿命短暂……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "所以就一直拖到现在了吗，\\n我倒觉得是咎由自取呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我记得，1000年前的封魔战争\\n也是人类不顾后果地\\n肆意破坏大自然导致的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "陆地上也可能会发生这种事。\\n与其说是种族的问题，\\n不如说是思考方式的问题。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "虽然说来惭愧……但说到底\\n人都是站着说话不腰疼的。\\n可能这就是世间常情吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "这样下去的话种族会灭亡。\\n所以才有人试图打破现状——\\n也就是侵略陆地吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "是的。作战已经迫在眉睫，\\n但我一定要阻止它！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族男子",
            "context": "蒂亚娜大人，您现在有时间吗？\\n我想找您商量一下今后的动向。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "知道了，我这就来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我说，蒂亚娜是什么身份啊？\\n看起来很受人尊敬呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "蒂亚娜大人是王国的公主，\\n同时也是“海神之巫女”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "她负责守护海神、\\n献上祈祷、赐予庇佑，\\n是至关重要的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "就是这个国家的大人物呗。\\n那为什么会住在这种民宅？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "因为蒂亚娜大人\\n被视作异端巫女，\\n从而被逐出了宫殿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "因为蒂亚娜大人\\n坚决反对侵略陆地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "她所提倡的既非侵略陆地，\\n也非接受灭亡，而是将海神大人\\n从沉睡中唤醒这一全新选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这不是很好吗？\\n哪里不行了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "利维坦沉睡时的呼吸\\n能为新的海域孕育新的生命。\\n所以不可将其唤醒……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "这就是福斯亚克的规矩。\\n但现在巫女却带头\\n试图破坏这个规矩……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "所以就被赶出来了啊。\\n不过她对侵略陆地派来说\\n也是个眼中钉吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "是啊，推崇侵略陆地的\\n是蒂亚娜的母亲，\\n也就是女王陛下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "那就是说，\\n蒂亚娜与亲生母亲对立，\\n然后被赶了出来！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "是的。但是蒂亚娜大人表现得\\n很坚强，为了保护子民与国家，\\n带领着我们前进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "既是叛变的巫女，\\n也是将大家团结到一起的人……\\n感觉跟某人很像呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "唉～一想到他，\\n就突然好想见他哦！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我们快点叫醒利维坦，\\n回到地面上吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "嗯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "这就是，沧海之钟……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯塔族女子",
            "context": "这是何等美丽，\\n堪比大海本身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "要敲响这口钟吗？\\n它会不会碎啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "不是的，只需要为它献上魔力，\\n会响的是大海。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "大海会回应祈祷，产生轰鸣。\\n据说那种声音听起来\\n就像钟声一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "总之试试看就知道了。\\n我们走吧，去利维坦那里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这就是，利维坦……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "要开始了哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "海发出轰鸣了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "拜托了，利维坦——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "怎、怎么回事！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这是怎么回事！？\\n也没有发起攻击，\\n但这股力量……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_10",
                "210002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "布伦希尔德",
            "context": "你们快到我身后来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120226_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "布伦希尔德",
            "context": "蒂亚娜，你也来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "海神利维坦！\\n如今，我们谢斯塔族\\n正面临着灭亡的危机！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "请再一次拯救我们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利维坦",
            "context": "你说……拯救？\\n我带给你们的只有毁灭。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "毁灭？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "你不是保护\\n谢斯塔族的神吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利维坦",
            "context": "我的力量乃波涛本身。\\n能吞噬世间万物，将其破坏殆尽。\\n我的存在本身便是罪过！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "怎么会是罪过呢！\\n毕竟在1000年前，\\n你拯救了海洋之民啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利维坦",
            "context": "波涛与波涛碰撞后\\n化为涟漪，仅此而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利维坦",
            "context": "可是我的危险性却不会改变。\\n所以我唯一能被饶恕的，\\n就是永远陷入沉睡。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120225_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "蒂亚娜",
            "context": "怎么会……那么，规矩其实\\n并不是为了保护新生命的诞生，\\n而是为了封印你的力量吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20834_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
